item.title: Botting as of 12/12/12
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

RsBot (powerbot) is up. I’d suggest you don’t use it if you want premium scripts or VIP. They are a money based company, like RuneScape. 99 days per premium license. Monthly cost for VIP. Only 1 way to pay.
EpicBot is also alive. They aren’t open source, but they work. They allow payment via GP, paypal, and other methods. It’s also a 1 time payment for permanent activation.

  • I’m currently botting Rocktail using PRO fisher on EpicBot.
    The only downside of epicbot is that the bot doesn’t know to restart the client then re-logg you. But if you set up timers, you can get a good 8-10 hours at a time.

Read full topic
